title: Soul Saga
description:
Ladies and gentlemen, for your consideration:

This torrent contains the entire run of  "Soul Saga" (issues 1 - 6) 

This short run series was Created, Written and Penciled by Stephen Platt. 

Issues 1-5 were published by Image/Top Cow. Issue #6 was released in Europe in a German edition, and recently surfaced as an English language scan. 



Thanks to the scanners and the original sources.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
